{"tid":2068604,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"係凍既地方出世你天生已經贏左","createTime":"2020-06-17T21:03:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-18T02:49:16.000Z","uid":58316,"like":3,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c1df34c82b93afc57cdf0b4618a3067fcc2e8edf","tid":2068604,"uid":58316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T21:03:44.000Z","msg":"天生凍既地方<br />\n就係世界既統治者<br />\n熱既地方只有乖乖進貢既份<br />\n以前蒙古鐵騎<br />\n女真人<br />\n唔識字冇文化但好打就夠<br />\n凍既地方窮極有個譜<br />\n印度真係唔夠中國打<br />\n南對北永遠都係北贏<br />\n連新德里都係北面<br />\n巴基斯坦首都搬上北面<br />\n因為連佢地都知越凍越着數<br />\n南京做左冇幾耐首都<br />\n又要搬上北京<br />\n台南又搬上台北<br />\n加州本來係墨西哥<br />\n東南亞政治經濟又俾華人控制<br />\n黑人d國家冇一個成氣候<br />\n依個世界<br />\n白真係好過黑<br />\n凍真係好過熱<br />\n有色人種<br />\n生活係熱個d地方既人<br />\n獨當一面註定失敗<br />\n唯有痴埋d凍既地方既人度<br />\n一係痴中國北方<br />\n一係痴英美<br />\n依個世界<br />\n好似真係有d人好命d<br />\n投胎去北歐加拿大最好命<br />\n中國北方次之<br />\n香港次之<br />\n最慘就赤道個d"},{"pid":"dd9f4c3b501281ce69efb8e5f9b3d63310120da7","tid":2068604,"uid":262482,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T21:12:39.000Z","msg":"即係格陵蘭統治緊世界？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88fe78cee849f4d289bb8fa062ef7d135eae2d48","tid":2068604,"uid":192465,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T21:15:45.000Z","msg":"潮文論冷熱南北"},{"pid":"2a1af6f99ada1c3a15de94dbabfa971fad7db92f","tid":2068604,"uid":103243,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T21:16:42.000Z","msg":"成日話香港濕凍世界第一<br />\n咁香港人統治咗世界未？"},{"pid":"c3732feffeefaee7b1323ce9488708443ee9d55f","tid":2068604,"uid":307619,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T21:16:48.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 借位一用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">[全人類請入] 投訴蘇文隆 唔好再俾條粉皮害手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2068154\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2068154</a></span></span></strong><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rNPeQ2w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrNPeQ2w.jpg&h=f4a8a3f6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/suBXOPc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsuBXOPc.jpg&h=39c942dc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EdP2ZVS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEdP2ZVS.png&h=1bd9e71b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有人會話法治已經死咗好撚耐<br />\n做呢啲嘢有撚用咩<br />\n<br />\n我唔知道做咗又冇用<br />\n我淨係知唔做就一定乜嘢都冇<br />\n<br />\n之前情操高尚嗰條粉皮暫時都冇得再審政治案件<br />\n都係多得各位手足堅持寫信投訴<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果唔想香港好嘅社工越來越少<br />\n如果唔想香港未來<br />\n得返一啲淨係識得幫新賤民呃公屋嘅社畜<br />\n如果唔想香港未來<br />\n未成年手足被藍屍社工出賣</span></span><br />\n唔該一人一信<br />\n保護一個為咗愛我地而失去左一年光陰<br />\n為咗愛香港而冒着釘牌危機都要行出嚟<br />\n<br />\n千祈唔好懶<br />\n依家輪到我哋愛佢了"},{"pid":"61e9b56883c64cf1de189664449763b889317d95","tid":2068604,"uid":351574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T22:18:42.000Z","msg":"Is Canada cold enough?"},{"pid":"5a7322ed7563f0420fac1f22190e1e9f7873d7f0","tid":2068604,"uid":157793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a1af6f99ada1c3a15de94dbabfa971fad7db92f","tid":2068604,"uid":103243,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T21:16:42.000Z","msg":"成日話香港濕凍世界第一<br />\n咁香港人統治咗世界未？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T22:43:59.000Z","msg":"其實老實講真係唔太覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51dad4dadffb95c3ea673e2393184d367bc23f51","tid":2068604,"uid":31200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T23:24:50.000Z","msg":"北極熊同企鵝點解統一唔到天下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f60cf85133059139807ea12cfdb834ef6d144172","tid":2068604,"uid":55458,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"dd9f4c3b501281ce69efb8e